      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Transport Commission (NTC) has decided to reduce the bus fares by 2.23% with effect from midnight today (19) in line with the recent fuel price reduction.",
        "Accordingly, the minimum bus fare has been brought down to Rs.38 from Rs.40. (Chaturanga Samarawickrama)"
